title: Batman RIP [h33t] [Alieneye]
description:
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batman_R.I.P." rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batman_R.I.P.</a>

This is a simple repack.  No one else has bothered to throw these together yet into a set yet though, so I figured I&#039;d post it. 

The Batman R.I.P. storyline crosses over on five Batman books, with a prequel in DC Universe #0. Keep in mind that the real end to this story-line will occur in the pages of Final Crisis.  Shortly after--presumably due to the aftermath of the complete storyline-- Nightwing, Robin, and Birds of Prey are being cancelled in January. 

Included here is:

DC Universe #0
Batman #676-681 
Detective Comics #846-850 
Nightwing #147-150 
Robin #175-176 
Batman and the Outsiders #11-13 

As always, Thanks to the original uploaders.

Enjoy.
